title: BBC R3 Documentary - 'The Moving Power of Art' sp7
description:
BBC R3 Sunday Feature - 'The Moving Power of Art'
Presented by Hisham Matar
Produced by Sandy Bowen
Broadcast March 2, 2008
Coded from tape at 128/44.1

In the week the New York Philharmonic Orchestra performed
in Pyongyang, North Korea, Radio 3 looked at how countries
use 'culture' as a political tool.

Contributers
Prof Joseph Nye
Neil MacGregor

http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=19346628" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
